<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>DevOps Project – Ansible Nginx</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Segoe UI", Arial, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a, #1e293b);
      color: #f1f5f9;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      height: 100vh;
    }

    .card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
      padding: 40px 50px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      text-align: center;
      width: 70%;
      max-width: 650px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: #38bdf8;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      margin-top: 0;
      color: #a5f3fc;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .team {
      margin-top: 28px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #fef3c7;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .hostname {
      margin-top: 12px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #cbd5e1;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="card">
    <h1>DevOps Project</h1>
    <h2>Automated Deployment with Ansible & Nginx</h2>

    <p>This webpage has been successfully deployed using <strong>Ansible</strong> 
    and is being served through <strong>Nginx</strong>.</p>

    <p class="team">Team Members – Oliver, Vivek, Navya</p>

    <p class="hostname">Server: {{ inventory_hostname }}</p>
  </div>
